":"Self-Reliance / Kujitegemea","importance":"Medium","expression":"Nyerere\'s philosophy of building from within; reducing dependency; local solutions","marketing_angle":"Local empowerment; \"made in Tanzania\" pride; building capacity; supporting Tanzanian solutions"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Ethnic harmony / national unity","importance":"Low","expression":"Very safe; Tanzania\'s peaceful coexistence is genuine point of pride; 120+ tribes without major conflict","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Serengeti and wildlife","importance":"Low","expression":"Safe; world-renowned conservation; natural heritage pride; responsible tourism angle","marketing_angle":""}]',
