ly; 10 November solemn","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Turkish cuisine","importance":"Low","expression":"Safe and positive; regional specialties; UNESCO intangible heritage; excellent for brand associations","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Scientific and cultural achievements","importance":"Low","expression":"Celebrate Turkish inventors, artists, writers; safe positive territory","marketing_angle":""}]',
