dentity; balance between tradition and modernity","marketing_angle":"Avoid extremes; balanced positioning; respect tradition while embracing progress; moderate tone"},{"value":"احترام الكبار (Respect for Elders)","importance":"Medium","expression":"Deference to parents, grandparents; \"حضرتك\" pronoun usage; seeking بركة (blessing) from elders","marketing_angle":"Show generational respect; consult parents in family purchase decisions; honor elderly in imagery"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Pharaonic heritage (الحضارة الفرعونية)","importance":"Low","expression":"Universal pride; pyramids, sphinx, temples; excellent for brand associations; ancient wisdom themes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Suez Canal","importance":"Low","expression":"Modern engineering achievement; national sovereignty symbol; 1956 and 2021 expansion pride","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"2011 and 2013 revolutions","importance":"High","expression":"Deeply divisive; avoid entirely; political sensitivities; different interpretations persist","marketing_angle":""}]',
