lopment; progress-oriented positioning; tech-forward appeals to aspirational consumers"},{"value":"Uzalendo (Patriotism)","importance":"Medium","expression":"Pride in Kenyan identity; support for local products; Buy Kenya Build Kenya initiatives; pride in international recognition","marketing_angle":"Local relevance messaging; Kenyan success stories; acknowledge national achievements; support local communities"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"M-Pesa Global Leadership","importance":"Low","expression":"Kenya pioneered mobile money; worldwide recognition; transformed financial inclusion; safe positive territory for fintech positioning","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Athletic Excellence","importance":"Low","expression":"Long-distance running dominance; Kipchoge, Keitany legends; national pride source; endurance metaphors resonate","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Multi-ethnic Unity","importance":"Medium","expression":"40+ ethnic groups coexisting; \"One Kenya\" aspirations; handle with care to avoid emphasizing division; focus on national identity","marketing_angle":""}]',
