ance":"Medium","expression":"Privacy respected; personal matters kept private; understated display of wealth or success","marketing_angle":"Respect privacy; avoid intrusive personalization; subtlety appreciated"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Culinaire erfgoed (Culinary heritage)","importance":"Low","expression":"Chocolate, beer, frieten, wafels; Belgian gastronomy world-renowned; safe and positive","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Cycling culture (wielrennen)","importance":"Low","expression":"Ronde van Vlaanderen, cycling heroes; deep cultural significance in Flanders","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"EU and international institutions","importance":"Low","expression":"Brussels as capital of Europe; pride in international role; diplomacy tradition","marketing_angle":""}]',
