t)","importance":"Medium","expression":"Pride in overcoming adversity; independence; resilience; Vietnamese identity","marketing_angle":"\"Hang Viet Nam chat luong cao\" (quality Vietnamese goods); national achievement themes"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Independence and reunification","importance":"Medium","expression":"Unification a source of pride; avoid war references that could divide; focus on peace and development","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Ao dai (traditional dress)","importance":"Low","expression":"National pride; elegant; appropriate for cultural celebrations and premium positioning","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Ho Chi Minh","importance":"Medium","expression":"Widely revered; use respectfully only; avoid commercial exploitation; historical respect","marketing_angle":""}]',
