ro","importance":"LOW","expression":"Safe to reference; symbol of natural beauty and achievement; Uhuru Peak represents freedom","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Zanzibar/Spice Islands","importance":"MEDIUM","expression":"Cultural gem but union with mainland can be sensitive; emphasize cultural richness, avoid political union topics","marketing_angle":""}]',
