garian-first content; never call it Slavic","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Thermal bath culture","importance":"Low","expression":"UNESCO heritage; healing tradition; safe for wellness and tourism contexts","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Hungarian cuisine","importance":"Low","expression":"Paprika, goulash, chimney cake; Tokaji wine; safe for food and hospitality contexts","marketing_angle":""}]',
