rtance":"Medium","expression":"Source of enormous pride; only country with Catalan official; celebrate without politicizing Catalunya-Spain dynamics","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Co-principality system","importance":"Low","expression":"Unique political system with two foreign co-princes; can reference as distinctive without taking political positions","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Romanesque heritage","importance":"Low","expression":"Medieval churches (Santa Coloma, Sant Joan de Caselles); UNESCO heritage; safe cultural reference","marketing_angle":""}]',
