ler privilegier l\'anglais ; eviter le franglais excessif","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Artistes quebecois","importance":"Low","expression":"References aux artistes locaux bienvenues ; musique, humour, cinema quebecois tres apprecies","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Hockey et sports d\'hiver","importance":"Low","expression":"Les Canadiens de Montreal sont une institution ; sports d\'hiver partie integrante de l\'identite","marketing_angle":""}]',
    c.communication_norms = '{"context_type":"LOW_CONTEXT","directness":"BALANCED","hierarchy_sensitivity":"LOW"}',
