ding; acknowledge seniority; religious sensitivities"},{"value":"Bersahaja (Humility)","importance":"Medium","expression":"Modest presentation; avoiding boastfulness; grounded despite success","marketing_angle":"Understated elegance; genuine quality over flashy claims; authenticity valued"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Malay as national language","importance":"Low","expression":"Constitutional status; proud heritage; national anthem in Malay; safe for references","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Multiracial harmony","importance":"Medium","expression":"Fundamental value; celebrate genuinely; avoid tokenism; show authentic inclusion","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Kampung heritage","importance":"Low","expression":"Nostalgic reference for older generation; authentic Malay Singaporean identity","marketing_angle":""}]',
