g; ethical branding; cultural authenticity; values alignment"},{"value":"समाजसेवा (Social Service)","importance":"Medium","expression":"Maharashtra\'s reformist tradition; Phule-Ambedkar legacy; social consciousness valued","marketing_angle":"Community benefit messaging; social responsibility; collective good themes; progressive positioning"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Shivaji Maharaj and Maratha Empire","importance":"High","expression":"Supreme respect required; never trivialize or commercialize; \"छत्रपती\" title mandatory; no casual use","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Marathi language and literature","importance":"Low","expression":"Safe celebration; अभिजात भाषा (classical language) status sought; literary heritage","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Pune as educational/IT hub","importance":"Low","expression":"Academic tradition; IT industry growth; \"Oxford of the East\" reference; startup ecosystem","marketing_angle":""}]',
