ence through quality; national achievement"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Эпос \"Манас\"","importance":"Low","expression":"World\'s longest epic poem; symbol of Kyrgyz identity and wisdom; safe to reference","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Кочевое наследие","importance":"Low","expression":"Юрты (боз уй), лошади, горная культура; authentic identity marker","marketing_angle":""}]',
