ource of national pride","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"民主自由 (Democracy and freedom)","importance":"Medium","expression":"Source of pride but can become political; use carefully without political statements","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"環保意識 (Environmental awareness)","importance":"Low","expression":"Taiwan\'s recycling and environmental efforts; safe positive reference","marketing_angle":""}]',
