pression":"Avoiding conflict; maintaining pleasant atmosphere; not embarrassing others publicly","marketing_angle":"Never shame or criticize publicly; offer face-saving solutions; maintain positive tone"},{"value":"Authenticity (Autenticidade)","importance":"Medium","expression":"Being genuine valued; \"gente de verdade\" appeals; fake or pretentious rejected","marketing_angle":"Real people, real stories; avoid overly polished or fake; authenticity beats perfection"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Football (Futebol)","importance":"Low","expression":"National passion; 5 World Cup titles; Pele, Neymar, etc.; safe and beloved reference","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Natural Beauty","importance":"Low","expression":"Amazon, beaches, biodiversity; environmental pride (though Amazon deforestation politically sensitive)","marketing_angle":""}]',
