ly life; religious holidays observed across traditions","marketing_angle":"Respectful acknowledgment; blessing language acceptable; sensitivity to religious diversity; never assume one faith"},{"value":"Family Loyalty","importance":"Medium","expression":"Strong family bonds; extended family important; multigenerational households common; family gatherings central","marketing_angle":"Family-centered messaging; multi-generational imagery; togetherness; Sunday family traditions"},{"value":"Entrepreneurial Spirit","importance":"Medium","expression":"Small business culture; \"hustle\" valued; side businesses common; making opportunities","marketing_angle":"Self-reliance messaging; building your own; entrepreneurship appeals; \"get up and get\" mentality"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Steelpan Invention","importance":"Low","expression":"National pride; only acoustic instrument invented in 20th century; safe positive reference; Panorama competition","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Brian Lara","importance":"Low","expression":"Greatest batsman; Test cricket record holder; national hero; safe sports reference; West Indies cricket pride","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Hasely Crawford","importance":"Low","expression":"First Olympic gold medallist (1976); national hero; athletic excellence; safe positive reference","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Republic Status (1976)","importance":"Low","expression":"Constitutional milestone; Ellis Clarke first President; point of pride; self-determination","marketing_angle":""}]',
