e); forward-looking","marketing_angle":"Innovation themes resonate; balance heritage with contemporary relevance"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Catalan language revival","importance":"Medium","expression":"Remarkable recovery after suppression; celebrate respectfully; acknowledge ongoing normalization efforts","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Gastronomic excellence","importance":"Low","expression":"Ferran Adria, traditional cuisine, cava; widely appreciated pride point","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Castells (Human towers)","importance":"Low","expression":"UNESCO heritage; symbol of cooperation and achievement; unifying and apolitical","marketing_angle":""}]',
