sial but prevalent)","marketing_angle":"Acknowledge effort; efficiency messaging; tools that help achieve more; respect for dedication"},{"value":"Collective Success (Jiti / 集体)","importance":"Medium","expression":"Group achievement over individual; company/nation pride; shared accomplishments","marketing_angle":"Team success stories; national pride connections; community achievements; \"together\" messaging"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Ancient civilization (5000 years)","importance":"Low","expression":"四大发明 (Four Great Inventions); cultural heritage; can reference proudly","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Technological advancement","importance":"Low","expression":"High-speed rail; space program; 5G; digital payments; legitimate pride points","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Sports achievements","importance":"Low","expression":"Olympics; specific athletes; national team successes","marketing_angle":""}]',
