":"Medium","expression":"Appreciation for quality, premium brands, status symbols; standing out positively","marketing_angle":"Premium positioning; exclusive offerings; VIP tiers; \"حصري\" (exclusive) messaging"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Liberation Day (26 February 1991)","importance":"Medium","expression":"Deep emotional significance; celebrate liberation, avoid graphic war imagery; gratitude to allies","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Kuwait Towers","importance":"Low","expression":"National landmark; positive symbol; use freely in Kuwaiti contexts","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Constitutional governance","importance":"Medium","expression":"Oldest parliament in Gulf; democratic traditions; use respectfully, not politically","marketing_angle":""}]',
