ssion":"Safe to celebrate; IKEA, Volvo, Spotify globally recognized; don\'t overstate","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Environmental leadership","importance":"Low","expression":"Genuine pride point; Greta Thunberg; recycling culture; climate action","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Nobel Prize","importance":"Low","expression":"Swedish heritage; internationally recognized; subtle references","marketing_angle":""}]',
