ression":"Group harmony; consensus-building; community and tribe connections","marketing_angle":"Community benefits emphasis; collective achievements; belonging and partnership language"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Two Holy Mosques (Makkah and Madinah)","importance":"HIGH","expression":"Sacred sites; never commercialise; only respectful references; no imagery in advertising","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Saudi Leadership","importance":"HIGH","expression":"Always speak respectfully; never criticise or satirise; formal protocol required","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Saudi Sports Achievements","importance":"LOW","expression":"Football success, hosting World Cup 2034; freely celebrate; positive brand associations","marketing_angle":""}]',
