nd viticulture","importance":"Low","expression":"Extremely positive; world-class wines; Cricova and Milestii Mici cellars; Wine Day celebration; safe to celebrate extensively","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Cultural heritage and traditions","importance":"Low","expression":"Folk arts, hora dance, traditional costumes, cuisine; safe to celebrate; shows respect for culture","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Language and Latin roots","importance":"Medium","expression":"Romanian language links to Latin heritage and European family; some prefer \"Moldovan language\" term; navigate carefully","marketing_angle":""}]',
