ession":"Local and regional pride; loyalty to hometown; regional identity often stronger than national; city rivalries and traditions","marketing_angle":"Regional authenticity; local sourcing; celebrate regional differences; avoid pan-Italian generalizations that ignore regional identity"},{"value":"Flessibilita","importance":"Medium","expression":"Adaptability; creative problem-solving; arrangiare (making do); improvisation; navigating complexity with ingenuity","marketing_angle":"Flexibility as service value; creative solutions; personal attention over rigid rules; accommodating customer needs"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Fashion and design (moda e design)","importance":"Low","expression":"Global leadership in fashion, furniture, automotive design; safe and positive; Milan as fashion capital","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Art and cultural heritage","importance":"Low","expression":"Renaissance, Roman Empire, museums, architecture; UNESCO World Heritage sites; cultural superpower status","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Automotive excellence","importance":"Low","expression":"Ferrari, Lamborghini, Maserati, Alfa Romeo, Vespa; design and engineering pride; safe positive references","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"European/EU membership","importance":"Medium","expression":"Generally positive but Euro debate exists; EU founding member; handle economic discussions carefully","marketing_angle":""}]',
