ck\"; reward effort messaging"},{"value":"Community Solidarity (Hromadska solidarnist)","importance":"High","expression":"Volunteer movements; mutual aid during crises; community networks; neighbor support","marketing_angle":"Community themes; collective action; \"together we are stronger\" messaging"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"2022+ defense of Ukraine","importance":"High","expression":"Deep national pride but also ongoing trauma; never trivialize; can reference strength and resilience respectfully; avoid war imagery in commercial contexts","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Maidan Revolution (2014)","importance":"Medium","expression":"\"Revolution of Dignity\"; pro-democracy symbol; positive reference but avoid commercialization","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Ukrainian cuisine","importance":"Low","expression":"Borshch (not borscht), varenyky, salo, pampushky beloved; safe for food contexts; borshch is Ukrainian, not Russian","marketing_angle":""}]',
