nce":"Low","expression":"Gagarin, space achievements universally celebrated; safe to reference","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Scientific achievements","importance":"Low","expression":"Mendeleev, Pavlov, contributions to physics and mathematics; well-received","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Winter/resilience imagery","importance":"Medium","expression":"Can resonate positively but avoid hardship stereotypes; focus on strength aspect","marketing_angle":""}]',
