rm on principles","marketing_angle":"Bold positioning; strength and reliability; resilience messaging"},{"value":"Wanaag (Goodness/Virtue)","importance":"Medium","expression":"Ethical behavior expected; honesty in dealings; helping those in need; charitable giving (zakat, sadaqa)","marketing_angle":"Ethical business practices; community giving; trustworthiness"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Somali language and poetry","importance":"Low","expression":"Pride in rich oral tradition; gabay poetry respected; safe cultural reference","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Mogadishu as historic trading city","importance":"Medium","expression":"Historical significance; current conditions sensitive; reference historical glory carefully","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Camel culture and pastoralism","importance":"Low","expression":"Deep cultural connection; camels symbol of wealth; safe positive reference","marketing_angle":""}]',
    c.communication_norms = '{"context_type":"HIGH_CONTEXT","directness":"INDIRECT","hierarchy_sensitivity":"HIGH"}',
    c.culture_summary = 'so-SO: Communication style is indirect. Hierarchy importance: high. Orientation: Collectivist (focus on \'we/together\'). Core values: Diinta Islaamka (Islam), Qoys (Family/Clan), Sharaf (Honor).',
