ng matters; avoiding shame (bejjat) essential; community opinion influential","marketing_angle":"Prestige positioning; status-conscious messaging; dignified communications; face-saving options"},{"value":"सहनशीलता (Tolerance)","importance":"Medium","expression":"Religious harmony valued; multi-ethnic coexistence; peaceful nature emphasized; Buddha\'s birthplace identity","marketing_angle":"Harmony themes; inclusive messaging; peace-oriented branding; diversity appreciation"},{"value":"Pride Point","importance":"Sensitivity","expression":"Usage Notes","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Mount Everest/Sagarmatha","importance":"Low","expression":"Safe; national symbol; \"top of the world\"; Nepali name \"Sagarmatha\" preferred; pride point","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Gurkha heritage","importance":"Low","expression":"Safe; global respect; bravery symbol; military tradition; khukuri symbolism","marketing_angle":""},{"value":"Hindu-Buddhist harmony","importance":"Low","expression":"Safe; religious coexistence model; syncretic culture; temple-stupa proximity","marketing_angle":""}]',
